headline: Dominion Energy Virginia Offers Energy-Saving Tips, Programs and Bill Payment Assistance for Winter
summary: This winter, Dominion Energy Virginia is reminding customers of simple energy-saving tips, as well as the programs that help customers save on their energy use and provide bill payment assistance for those in need.

headline: Enbridge: I Am Not Impressed With The Recent Dividend Increase
